                "name": "Spikes",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "With a snap of its tail, a manticore can loose a volley of four spikes as a standard action (make an attack roll for each spike). This attack has a range of 180 feet with no range increment. All targets must be within 30 feet of each other. The creature can launch only 24 spikes in any 24-hour period."
